A.ORDER_DATE) AS GWA , A.YYYYMM AS YYYYMM , A.DONBOK_YN AS DONBOK_YN , A.IN_OUT_GUBUN AS IN_OUT_GUBUN , A.MIX_GROUP AS MIX_GROUP , A.HO_CODE AS HO_CODE , A.DV_TIME AS DV_TIME , A.DV AS DV , DECODE(C.HANGMOG_CODE, NULL , 'N', 'Y') AS ANTIBIOTIC_YN , A.MAGAM_GUBUN|| A.ORDER_DATE || A.GROUP_SER || A.MIX_GROUP|| LTRIM(TO_CHAR(A.SEQ, '0000000000')) CONT_KEY , DECODE(A.NUM01, '0', null, DECODE(A.NUM17, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM17 , DECODE(A.NUM18, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM18 , DECODE(A.NUM19, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM27 , DECODE(A.NUM28, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM28 , DECODE(A.NUM29, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM29 , DECODE(A.NUM30, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM30 , DECODE(A.NUM31, '0', null, DECODE(A.MAGAM_GUBUN, 'ZZ', '○','●')) AS NUM31 FROM (-- 抗生剤 薬、注射 SELECT C.HANGMOG_CODE FROM OCS0103 C , INV0110 A WHERE C.HOSP_CODE = 'K01' AND C.WONNAE_DRG_YN = 'Y' AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND C.END_DATE AND A.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND A.JAERYO_CODE = C.HANGMOG_CODE AND A.SMALL_CODE LIKE '61%' ) C , OUT0101 B , DRG9005 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.YYYYMM = :f_yyyymm AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND C.HANGMOG_CODE (+)= A.JAERYO_CODE ORDER BY CONT_KEY

data.name: grdPalist.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT E.HO_DONG1 , E.HO_CODE1 , E.BED_NO , E.BUNHO , E.SUNAME , E.PKINP1001 , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE('2013/09/20',E.BIRTH,'')||'/'||E.SEX AGE_SEX , E.IPWON_DATE IPWON_DATE , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(E.DOCTOR, TO_DATE('2013/09/20', 'YYYY/MM/DD')) DOCTOR_NAME , D.HO_SORT FROM BAS0250 D , VW_OCS_INP1001 E WHERE E.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND E.HO_DONG1 LIKE :f_ho_dong AND D.HOSP_CODE = E.HOSP_CODE AND D.HO_DONG = E.HO_DONG1 AND D.HO_CODE = E.HO_CODE1 AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN D.START_DATE AND D.END_DATE ORDER BY E.HO_DONG1, D.HO_SORT, E.BED_NO
